msgstr "#### 仅生成（不构建完整站点）"

msgid ""
"By default, artifacts are written to: "
"`docs/_build/doc_codegen/<doc_stem>/<block_name>.sh`."
msgstr "默认情况下，生成物会写入：`docs/_build/doc_codegen/<doc_stem>/<block_name>.sh`。"

