msgid "### For developers: add a new converter"
msgstr "### 面向开发者：添加新的转换器"

msgid ""
"A converter turns one loaded YAML file plus one parsed `ModelCodeBlock` into a\n"
"`GeneratedScript`. The current pipeline is:"
msgstr ""
"转换器将一个已加载的 YAML 文件和一个解析后的 `ModelCodeBlock` 转换为\n"
"`GeneratedScript`。当前的流程如下："

msgid ""
"1. `BlockScanner` parses ``model-code`` fences and accepts only options listed\n"
"   in `MODEL_CODE_OPTION_NAMES`.\n"
"2. `YamlLoader` loads `test_case_path`.\n"
"3. `get_converter()` looks up `block.converter_tag` from\n"
"   `build_default_converters()`.\n"
"4. The selected converter returns `GeneratedScript(content=..., language=\"shell\")`.\n"
"5. `GeneratorService` replaces `{{ generated }}` in the block body, validates\n"
"   that the final script is non-empty, and writes\n"
"   `docs/_build/doc_codegen/<doc_stem>/<block_name>.sh`."
msgstr ""
"1. `BlockScanner` 解析 ``model-code`` 围栏，仅接受 `MODEL_CODE_OPTION_NAMES` 中列出的选项。\n"
"2. `YamlLoader` 加载 `test_case_path`。\n"
"3. `get_converter()` 从 `build_default_converters()` 中查找 `block.converter_tag`。\n"
"4. 选定的转换器返回 `GeneratedScript(content=..., language=\"shell\")`。\n"
"5. `GeneratorService` 替换块体中的 `{{ generated }}`，验证最终脚本非空，并写入\n"
"   `docs/_build/doc_codegen/<doc_stem>/<block_name>.sh`。"

msgid "To add a converter:"
msgstr "要添加转换器，请执行以下步骤："

msgid ""
"1. In `tools/docs_codegen/converters.py`, add a `BaseConverter` subclass with a\n"
"   unique `name`. That name is the value authors put in `:converter_tag:`.\n"
"2. Implement `convert(self, loaded_yaml, *, block) -> GeneratedScript`. Use\n"
"   `make_docs_codegen_error(..., block=block)` for user-facing validation\n"
"   errors so the CLI and Sphinx output include document context.\n"
"3. Reuse helpers from `tools/docs_codegen/utils.py`, such as\n"
"   `require_mapping`, `require_mapping_list`, `require_scalar_mapping`,\n"
"   `require_indexed_mapping`, `require_node_field`, `parse_command_tokens`,\n"
"   `substitute_template_positionals`, and `render_cli_command`.\n"
"4. Register the converter in `build_default_converters()`. If it is not\n"
"   registered, `get_converter()` will reject the new `converter_tag`.\n"
"5. If the converter needs new directive metadata, add the option name to\n"
"   `MODEL_CODE_OPTION_NAMES` in `tools/docs_codegen/scanner.py` and to\n"
"   `ModelCodeDirective.option_spec` in\n"
"   `tools/docs_codegen/sphinx_extension.py`. Read the option with\n"
"   `block.get_option(\"<option_name>\")`.\n"
"6. Add or update tests in `tests/ut/tools/test_docs_codegen.py`. Cover the\n"
"   successful render path, required option validation, YAML shape validation,\n"
"   and any CLI/Sphinx scanner behavior affected by new metadata.\n"
"7. Add a real ``model-code`` example in a model tutorial, preferably under\n"
"   `docs/source/tutorials/models/`, and point it to an existing YAML file under\n"
"   `tests/`.\n"
"8. Validate with the CLI:"
msgstr ""
"1. 在 `tools/docs_codegen/converters.py` 中添加一个 `BaseConverter` 子类，并赋予唯一的 `name`。该名称即作者在 `:converter_tag:` 中填入的值。\n"
"2. 实现 `convert(self, loaded_yaml, *, block) -> GeneratedScript`。对于面向用户的验证错误，请使用 `make_docs_codegen_error(..., block=block)`，以便 CLI 和 Sphinx 输出包含文档上下文。\n"
"3. 复用 `tools/docs_codegen/utils.py` 中的辅助函数，例如 `require_mapping`、`require_mapping_list`、`require_scalar_mapping`、`require_indexed_mapping`、`require_node_field`、`parse_command_tokens`、`substitute_template_positionals` 和 `render_cli_command`。\n"
"4. 在 `build_default_converters()` 中注册该转换器。如果未注册，`get_converter()` 将拒绝新的 `converter_tag`。\n"
"5. 如果转换器需要新的指令元数据，请将选项名称添加到 `tools/docs_codegen/scanner.py` 中的 `MODEL_CODE_OPTION_NAMES`，以及 `tools/docs_codegen/sphinx_extension.py` 中的 `ModelCodeDirective.option_spec`。使用 `block.get_option(\"<option_name>\")` 读取该选项。\n"
"6. 在 `tests/ut/tools/test_docs_codegen.py` 中添加或更新测试。覆盖成功渲染路径、必需选项验证、YAML 形状验证，以及受新元数据影响的任何 CLI/Sphinx 扫描器行为。\n"
"7. 在模型教程中添加一个真实的 ``model-code`` 示例，最好放在 `docs/source/tutorials/models/` 下，并将其指向 `tests/` 下已有的 YAML 文件。\n"
"8. 使用 CLI 进行验证："

msgid ""
"If a converter should render something other than shell, set\n"
"`GeneratedScript.language` accordingly so Sphinx can highlight the generated\n"
"literal block correctly."
msgstr ""
"如果转换器应渲染非 Shell 的内容，请相应地设置\n"
"`GeneratedScript.language`，以便 Sphinx 能够正确高亮生成的文字块。"

msgid "Write the doc block like this:"
msgstr "请按如下方式编写文档块："

msgid ""
"set -eux\n"
"{{ generated }}"
msgstr ""
"set -eux\n"
"{{ generated }}"

msgid "| converter_tag | Renders | YAML source |"
msgstr "| converter_tag | 渲染结果 | YAML 源 |"

msgid "| Option | Required | Description |"
msgstr "| 选项 | 是否必需 | 描述 |"

msgid "| Template variable | Rendered positional |"
msgstr "| 模板变量 | 渲染后的位置 |"

msgid ""
"| `single_node` | A single node's env exports + `vllm serve` script | "
"`test_cases[case_index]` |"
msgstr ""
"| `single_node` | 单节点的环境导出 + `vllm serve` 脚本 | `test_cases[case_index]` |"

msgid ""
"| `multi_node` | One host's env exports + `vllm serve` script | "
"`deployment[host_index]` |"
msgstr ""
"| `multi_node` | 一个主机的环境导出 + `vllm serve` 脚本 | `deployment[host_index]` |"

msgid ""
"| `external_dp_template` | One external-DP node's env exports + `vllm serve`"
" command | `templates[host_index]` |"
msgstr ""
"| `external_dp_template` | 一个外部 DP 节点的环境导出 + `vllm serve` 命令 | "
"`templates[host_index]` |"

msgid ""
"| `external_dp_launch` | One `launch_online_dp.py` line per node | "
"`config[]` |"
msgstr "| `external_dp_launch` | 每个节点一行 `launch_online_dp.py` | `config[]` |"

msgid ""
"| `external_dp_proxy` | The load-balance proxy launch command | `config[]` +"
" `routing` |"
msgstr "| `external_dp_proxy` | 负载均衡代理的启动命令 | `config[]` + `routing` |"

msgid ""
"| `block_name` | Yes | Block name; must be unique within the current "
"document |"
msgstr "| `block_name` | 是 | 块名称；在当前文档内必须唯一 |"

msgid "| `converter_tag` | Yes | Selects one of the built-in converters |"
msgstr "| `converter_tag` | 是 | 选择一个内置转换器 |"

msgid ""
"| `test_case_path` | Yes | Repository-relative YAML path that stays within "
"the repo; the file must exist |"
msgstr "| `test_case_path` | 是 | 仓库相对路径的 YAML 路径，必须在仓库内；文件必须存在 |"

msgid "| `${VISIBLE_DEVICES}` | `$1` |"
msgstr "| `${VISIBLE_DEVICES}` | `$1` |"

msgid "| `${PORT}` | `$2` |"
msgstr "| `${PORT}` | `$2` |"

msgid "| `${DP_SIZE}` | `$3` |"
msgstr "| `${DP_SIZE}` | `$3` |"

msgid "| `${DP_RANK}` | `$4` |"
msgstr "| `${DP_RANK}` | `$4` |"

msgid "| `${DP_ADDRESS}` | `$5` |"
msgstr "| `${DP_ADDRESS}` | `$5` |"

msgid "| `${DP_RPC_PORT}` | `$6` |"
msgstr "| `${DP_RPC_PORT}` | `$6` |"

msgid "| `${TP_SIZE}` | `$7` |"
msgstr "| `${TP_SIZE}` | `$7` |"
